### TSQR Tool Library API — Sample Requests

### Public (no auth required)

GET {{Host}}/api/tools?page=1&pageSize=20
GET {{Host}}/api/tools/1
GET {{Host}}/api/tools/stats
GET {{Host}}/api/dashboard/stats
GET {{Host}}/api/manufacturers

### Authenticated (requires Bearer token from tsqr-autheo)

POST {{Host}}/api/tools/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Test Tool",
  "description": "A test tool",
  "manufacturerId": 1,
  "toolType": 1,
  "amortizationRate": 1,
  "ownerId": 1,
  "serialNumber": "TEST-001",
  "initialCondition": 2
}

###

POST {{Host}}/api/members/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "middleName": "",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "age": 30,
  "address": "123 Main St",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "555-0100",
  "status": 1
}

###

POST {{Host}}/api/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "memberId": 2,
  "reservationDate": "2026-07-15"
}

###

GET {{Host}}/api/members?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

GET {{Host}}/api/inventory?pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}